## Dependency Injection & Extensions

### DependencyInjection.cs Pattern
Every layer has a `DependencyInjection.cs` file:

```csharp
namespace GoalifyNow.Auth.Infrastructure;

public static class DependencyInjection
{
    public static IServiceCollection AddInfrastructure(
        this IServiceCollection services,
        IConfiguration configuration)
    {
        services.AddSoftDeleteInterceptor();
        services.AddCommonDbContext<AuthDbContext>(configuration);
        services.AddOutboxDispatcher<AuthDbContext>();
        services.Configure<StripeOptions>(configuration.GetSection(StripeOptions.SectionName));
        services.AddScoped<IReplayProtectionService, InMemoryReplayProtectionService>();
        return services;
    }
}
```

### Common Services Registration
```csharp
// In Program.cs
builder.AddGoalifyNowCommonServices(options =>
{
    options.UseCloudIntegration = true;
    options.UseGrpcServer = true;
    options.UseMessaging = true;
    options.UseDomainEventPublishing = true;
    options.UseSqlDatabase = true;
    options.UseAzureStorage = true;
    options.UseApiConfiguration = true;
    options.UseGrpcAuthValidation = true;
});
```

### gRPC Configuration
```csharp
// gRPC server
builder.AddGrpcServer();
app.MapGrpcService<ClaimsGrpcService>();

// gRPC clients
builder.Services.AddAuthGrpcClient(builder.Configuration);
builder.Services.AddGrpcClient<PropertyService.PropertyServiceClient>(Configuration, "Property");
```

