## Project Conventions

### Folder Structure
```
GoalifyNow.{ServiceName}/
├── GoalifyNow.{ServiceName}.API/
│   ├── Controllers/
│   ├── Services/
│   ├── Options/
│   └── Program.cs
├── GoalifyNow.{ServiceName}.Application/
│   ├── Features/{FeatureName}/
│   │   ├── Commands/
│   │   ├── Queries/
│   │   ├── Services/
│   │   ├── Validators/
│   │   └── Options/
│   └── DependencyInjection.cs
├── GoalifyNow.{ServiceName}.Domain/
│   ├── Entities/
│   ├── Events/
│   ├── ValueObjects/
│   └── Enums/
└── GoalifyNow.{ServiceName}.Infrastructure/
    ├── Persistence/
    ├── Options/
    └── DependencyInjection.cs
```

### Always Use ProjectReference (Never PackageReference for Shared Libraries)
```xml
<ItemGroup>
  <!-- CORRECT -->
  <ProjectReference Include="..\..\..\shared\GoalifyNow.Common.API\GoalifyNow.Common.API.csproj" />
  
  <!-- INCORRECT -->
  <PackageReference Include="GoalifyNow.Common.API" Version="1.0.0" />
</ItemGroup>
```

